high_descs: Turn left and walk to the stove then take a tiny step to your right.
Pick up the frying pan that's in front of you on the front right burner.
Turn around and walk to the wall then turn left and walk to the fridge.
Chill the pan in the fridge then get it back out and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the wall then turn right.
Put the pan to the left of the knife and under it with the handle pointing left.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold pan on the table.

high_descs: Walk to the white stove on the left.
Pick up the black pan on the front right corner of the stove.
Turn around and walk to the fridge on the left.
Put the pan on the top shelf inside the fridge, chill it for seven seconds, remove it and close the door.
Turn around and turn right at the wall to face the side of the white table.
Put the chilled pan on the table to the left of the knife with the yellow handle.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled pan on a table.

high_descs: Turn left and stop at the oven
Grab the pan from the bottom right stove
Turn around and go to the fridge
Put the pan in the fridge and close the door. Then take the pan out
Turn around and go to the white table
Put the pan on the table
anns.task_desc: Putting a pan on the white table
